    • composite

      @API(status=EXPERIMENTAL, since="6.0") static TestDescriptor.Visitor composite(TestDescriptor.Visitor... visitors)
      Combine the supplied visitors into a single Visitor.

      If the supplied array contains only a single Visitor, that Visitor is returned as is.

      Parameters:
      visitors - the Visitors to combine; never null or empty
      Returns:
      the combined Visitor
      Throws:
      PreconditionViolationException - if visitors is null, contains null elements, or is empty
      Since:
      1.13
